import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Grid, Box } from '@mui/material';
import VerifiedUserIcon from '@mui/icons-material/VerifiedUser';
import TrendingUpIcon from '@mui/icons-material/TrendingUp';
import SecurityIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Security';

function HighlightsSection() {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ paddingY: 8 }}>
      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Box textAlign="center">
            <VerifiedUserIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#007bff', marginBottom: 2 }} />
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#333333', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Trusted Tournaments
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#6c757d' }}>
              Participate in the most trusted and verified online fishing tournaments.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Box textAlign="center">
            <TrendingUpIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#007bff', marginBottom: 2 }} />
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#333333', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Real-Time Scoring
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#6c757d' }}>
              Track your progress with real-time leaderboards and scoring.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Box textAlign="center">
            <SecurityIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#007bff', marginBottom: 2 }} />
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#333333', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Secure Transactions
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#6c757d' }}>
              Safely deposit and withdraw your earnings with our secure payment system.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default HighlightsSection;
